# ── Where Am I – environment variables ────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your own values.
# .env is git-ignored and must never be committed.
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_* variables are embedded into the JavaScript bundle at build time
# and are readable by client-side code.  Keep secrets out of these variables.

# OpenStreetMap (Nominatim, Overpass) — free services, no API key required!
# Map tiles, reverse geocoding, and POI search use OSM data.

